OL,3,CHottest year on record: 2024 was first
OL,4,Cyear to break 1.5C warming threshold
OL,6,FExperts from the EU's Copernicus
OL,7,FClimate Change Service said
OL,8,Funprecedented heatwaves and extreme
OL,9,Frainfall caused misery for millions,
OL,10,FITV News Correspondent Geraint Vincent
OL,11,Freports
OL,13,FLast year was the hottest on record
OL,14,Fand the first to breach a key global
OL,15,Fwarming threshold of 1.5C above pre-
OL,16,Findustrial temperatures, scientists
OL,17,Fhave said.
