OL,3,CHottest year on record: 2024 was first
OL,4,Cyear to break 1.5C warming threshold
OL,6,FBut the record heat should be a
OL,7,F"reality check" with a year of extreme
OL,8,Fweather events showing how dangerous
OL,9,Flife with 1.5C of warming was, one
OL,10,Fexpert said.
OL,12,FPursuing efforts to prevent the world
OL,13,Fwarming more than 1.5C above pre-
OL,14,Findustrial temperatures is one of the
OL,15,Fkey commitments of the global Paris
OL,16,Ftreaty which countries agreed to in
OL,17,F2015, in a bid to avert the most
OL,18,Fdangerous impacts of climate change.
