OL,3,CHottest year on record: 2024 was first
OL,4,Cyear to break 1.5C warming threshold
OL,6,FThe UK analysis found that the global
OL,7,Faverage temperature in 2024 was 1.53C
OL,8,Fabove the 1850-1900 average, with a
OL,9,Fmargin of error of plus or minus
OL,10,F0.08C, making it likely the first
OL,11,Fcalendar year to exceed 1.5C.
OL,13,FIt was also the 11th year in
OL,14,Fsuccession in the data series that has
OL,15,Fequalled or exceeded 1C above pre-
OL,16,Findustrial levels.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
