OL,3,CHottest year on record: 2024 was first
OL,4,Cyear to break 1.5C warming threshold
OL,6,FColin Morice of the Met Office said:
OL,7,F"A single year exceeding 1.5C above
OL,8,Fpre-industrial does not mean a breach
OL,9,Fof the Paris Agreement 1.5C guard rail
OL,10,F` that would require a temperature of
OL,11,Fat least 1.5C on average over a longer
OL,12,Fperiod.
OL,14,F"However, it does show that the
OL,15,Fheadroom to avoid an exceedance of
OL,16,F1.5C, over a sustained period, is now
OL,17,Fwafer thin."
