OL,4,Cyear to break 1.5C warming threshold
OL,6,FSamantha Burgess, from the European
OL,7,FCentre for Medium-Range Weather
OL,8,FForecasts (ECMWF) which runs C3S,
OL,9,Fsaid: "We are now teetering on the
OL,10,Fedge of passing the 1.5C level defined
OL,11,Fin the Paris Agreement and the average
OL,12,Fof the last two years is already above
OL,13,Fthis level.
OL,15,F"These high global temperatures,
OL,16,Fcoupled with record global atmospheric
OL,17,Fwater vapour levels in 2024, meant
OL,18,Funprecedented heatwaves and heavy
OL,19,Frainfall events, causing misery for
OL,20,Fmillions of people."
