OL,6,F"This notable landmark further
OL,7,Fhighlights the urgency of efforts to
OL,8,Fminimise future warming."
OL,10,FIn response to the announcement, Dr
OL,11,FFriederike Otto, senior lecturer at
OL,12,Fthe Centre for Environmental Policy,
OL,13,FImperial College London, said: "This
OL,14,Frecord needs to be a reality check.
OL,16,F"The climate is heating to levels
OL,17,Fwe've spent years trying to avoid
OL,18,Fbecause countries are still burning
OL,19,Fhuge amounts of oil, gas and coal. A
OL,20,Fyear of extreme weather showed just
OL,21,Fhow dangerous life is at 1.5C.
